<!-- HERO / Brand story -->
<section class="sn-page-hero">
  <span class="sn-page-hero__eyebrow">Our story</span>
  <h1 class="sn-page-hero__title">Built out of <em>frustration</em><br>with the skincare aisle.</h1>
  <p class="sn-page-hero__lead">Hisae started because skincare shopping is broken. The aisle is a lottery — a thousand bottles, each promising miracles, none designed with your actual skin in mind. Half the time you end up reacting, the other half you can't tell if anything's working.</p>
  <p class="sn-page-hero__lead">We're a small, founder-led brand. We built the quiz because the right routine for you depends on your actual skin — your type, your concerns, your sensitivity, and what you already use. Every product in our catalogue is one we'd use ourselves, at clinically meaningful percentages, with full INCI ingredient lists on every page.</p>
  <p class="sn-page-hero__lead">No inflated customer counts, no fake reviews — just formulas we stand behind, and a quiz that actually listens.</p>
</section>

