      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="sn-page-section sn-page-section--narrow" id="faq">
  <h2 class="sn-page-section__title"><em>Frequently</em> asked.</h2>
  <div class="sn-page-faq">
    <details class="sn-page-faq__item" open>
      <summary class="sn-page-faq__q">
        <span class="sn-page-faq__q-text">How does the personalised quiz work?</span>
        <span class="sn-page-faq__icon">+</span>
      </summary>
      <p class="sn-page-faq__a">The quiz takes under 60 seconds. It asks about your skin type, top concern, current routine, SPF habits, and any history of reactions. Based on your answers, we match you with a 2–4 product routine — Essential, Recommended, or Complete.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="sn-page-faq__item">
      <summary class="sn-page-faq__q">
        <span class="sn-page-faq__q-text">Can I buy individual products instead of a full routine?</span>
        <span class="sn-page-faq__icon">+</span>
      </summary>
      <p class="sn-page-faq__a">Absolutely. The quiz results page shows each product individually with its own add-to-cart button. Routines are just a curated shortcut — nothing is gated behind them.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="sn-page-faq__item">
      <summary class="sn-page-faq__q">
        <span class="sn-page-faq__q-text">How long until I see results?</span>
        <span class="sn-page-faq__icon">+</span>
      </summary>
      <p class="sn-page-faq__a">Hydrating and calming products usually feel different on day one. Brightening and anti-aging actives take 2–4 weeks to show visible changes, with full benefits building over 6–8 weeks of consistent use.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="sn-page-faq__item">
      <summary class="sn-page-faq__q">
        <span class="sn-page-faq__q-text">Are your products safe for sensitive skin?</span>
        <span class="sn-page-faq__icon">+</span>
      </summary>
      <p class="sn-page-faq__a">Several of our formulas are built specifically for reactive skin — fragrance-free, acid-free, and free of common irritants. The quiz flags products that suit sensitive skin. Always patch test before first use, and consult a dermatologist for severe skin conditions.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="sn-page-faq__item">
      <summary class="sn-page-faq__q">
        <span class="sn-page-faq__q-text">What's your shipping and returns policy?</span>
        <span class="sn-page-faq__icon">+</span>
      </summary>
      <p class="sn-page-faq__a">Free US shipping on orders over $50. Orders typically arrive in 5–10 business days. Every product is covered by our 30-day money-back guarantee — if it doesn't work for your skin, we refund you, no questions asked.</p>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

